cu.explanation_en: Changing the NG-AMF interface IP address to a different subnet (10.0.0.43) creates an unreachable IP range conflict, preventing CU-AMF NG interface communication and causing connection failures.

du.explanation_en: Altering the local network address to an unreachable subnet (192.168.80.3) introduces routing misconfiguration, preventing DU from establishing proper network connections and leading to interface failures.
